To start the App, run `node server.mjs` in terminal.

server.mjs is the starting point. It contains all the API end points.

db.db is the database file. It can be accessed by opening it in DB Browser (SQLite) desktop application (https://sqlitebrowser.org/).

Web scraper:
To extract new music events from the web, run `node web-scraper/scrape_events_and_update_db.mjs` in terminal.
